{"id":"rehabiah","term":"Rehabiah","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Enlargement of the Lord, the son of Eliezer, and grandson of Moses (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 23:17\">1 Chr. 23:17</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 24:21\">24:21</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["1 Chronicles 23:17","1 Chronicles 24:21"]}